descp2: An iterable containing the FeatureColumns to use as inputs to your model. All items should be instances of classes derived from `DenseColumn` such as `numeric_column`, `embedding_column`,`bucketized_column`, `indicator_column`. If you have categorical features, you can wrap them with an `embedding_column` or`indicator_column`.
